equipa.guilherme_vieira.bio:
Twenty-one years of experience in national and multinational companies in the Information and Communication Technology (ICT) sector, eighteen of which supporting organizational changes involving complex business processes;

Solid commercial and business development experience acquired through extensive experience in negotiating ICT solutions (software, hardware and services) in the southeast, northeast, south and central-west regions of Brazil;

Consistent performance and knowledge in all phases of the sales cycle for public and private organizations.<br> Proficiency in the main modalities and types of public and private acquisitions such as RFI, RFP, RFQ, bidding, auction, lowest price, technical and price, price registration system, among others;
